  "Call this site’s live mock endpoint": "Vhidza muṋe wa khumbelo wa u linga wa webu heyi u re na tshumelo",
  "Can AI Be a Moral Victim? Ownership and Moral Patiency in Everyday Judgments": "Can AI Be a Moral Victim? Ownership and Moral Patiency in Everyday Judgments",
  "Can AI learn from this? To what depth, for which uses, with what obligations?": "Naa AI i nga guda kha hezwi? Nga vhuenda hafhio, nga mishumo ifhio, na mishumo ifhio ya vhuḓifhinga?",
  "Can We Ever Understand Consciousness?": "Can We Ever Understand Consciousness?",
