  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Tsumbo dza kodo, JSON Schemas, na maitele a mulayo ane mishini ya kona u a vhala zwo laisenisiwa fhasi ha Laisenisi ya MIT nga nnḓa ha musi zwo ambiwa nga inwe nḓila. Ni nga a shumisa kha webu dzaṋu nga mahala.",
  "Combined rights entry point": "Muṋe wa u dzhena wo ṱanganywaho wa pfanelo",
  "Commercial Redistribution": "U Phaḓalatsha nga Bindu",
  "Commercial use": "U shumisa nga bindu",
  "Commercial use requires contact": "U shumisa nga bindu zwi ṱoḓa kwamano",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Yo humbelwa nga murahu ha Buthano ḽa Tsireledzo ya AI ḽa Bletchley na u langwa nga Yoshua Bengio na vhaḓivhi vhu fhiraho 100 vha tshi bva kha shango dzi sekaho 30 na UN, OECD na EU, muvhigo uyu u ḓiimisaho u ṱanganya vhuṱanzi ha saintsi ha zwino nga ha vhukoni na khombo dza AI ya nṱha — u tshi sumbedza uri zwiṅwe zwiimiswa zwino zwi nga topola musi zwi tshi khou linganyiswa nahone zwa shandukisa vhuḓifari hazwo zwi tshi ya ngazwo.",
  "Companion media": "Zwibveledzwa zwo tshimbidzanaho",
  "Compensation models tied to learning depth": "Mbekanyo dza mbadelo dzo bofhaho kha vhuenda ha u guda",
  "Conditions (comma-separated)": "Milayo (yo fhambanywaho nga khoma)",
